# Changelog

All notable changes to the OS Age Reporter project will be documented in this file.

## 2025-07-29

### Added
- Added documentation header to the script with usage information, author, date, and changelog
- Created initial CHANGELOG file to track project changes

### Changed
- Updated config.json format (email_recipient is now a string instead of an array)
- Moved config.json to project root directory for easier access (previously expected at ~/.config/os-age-report/config.json)
- Sanitized config.json